files.description:
Stata dataset containing treatment assignment, actual enrollments, outcomes, and covariates on students enrolled in the the Tennessee STAR experiment. This dataset is a simple conversion to Stata format of the publicly available dataset STAR_Students.tab located at https://dataverse.harvard.edu/dataset.xhtml?persistentId=hdl:1902.1/10766. A detailed description of the data can be found at the dataverse URL in the previous sentence, but the following are the variables used in the analysis for this paper:
gkfreelunch: indicator for the student being eligible for free or reduced-priced lunch (an indicator of low parental income)
gkclasstype: indicator for treatment assignment. This variable equals 1 when the student was assigned to a small class in kindergarten
g1tmathss: score on 1st grade math assessment; our main outcome variable
files.label: STAR_Students.tab
